PRO NCDF_DATA::OpenFile, filename
;+
; NAME:
;       NCDF_DATA::OpenFile
;
; PURPOSE:
;
;       This method is used to open a new netCDF or HDF file and add it to the object.
;
; CALLING SEQUENCE:
;
;       IDL> nCDFObject -> OpenFile, filename
;
; ARGUMENTS:
;
;       filename:  The name of a netCDF or HDF file to open.
;
; KEYWORD PARAMETERS:
